    • addScreening

      public void addScreening(int cinema, String MovieName, Date showingDate, TypeOfMovie typeOfMovie) throws Exception
      It creates a screeening showtime after a cineplex has been chosen by main It passes in which cinema to put it in, the movie to screen, the date that it will show and the type of movie it is. Uses cinema class to create a showtime to store in cinema side and it also add showtime on the cineplex side list too. Provides as a checker to check if screening has been added too.
      Parameters:
      cinema - cinema name passed in as an integer.
      MovieName - movie name passed in as a string.
      showingDate - date and time of showing to be created as a Date object.
      typeOfMovie - Type of movie whether 3D or digital passed in as a TypeOfMovie.
      Throws:
      Exception

    • addCineplexList

      public boolean addCineplexList(String MovieName) throws Exception
      Adds movie in cineplex master list for what is currently being screened at the cineplex. Adds to screenings to prepare to take in screening showtime too.
      Parameters:
      MovieName - Movie name to be added into the cineplex master list for current screening as a string format.
      Returns:
      A boolean of whether adding to the cineplex master list of movies is successful or not.
      Throws:
      Exception

    • searchMovies

      private int searchMovies(String MovieName)

      Parameters:
      MovieName - movie name to search for in cineplex movie showing list passed in as a string
      Returns:
      returns index if it is found which is more than 0 if not it will return -1 if it is not inside.
